# Rely Design System

- Keep reusable tokens, providers, and UI primitives in `shared/design-system`.
- Do not couple the design system to a concrete auth provider.
- App-specific navigation, feature cards, station widgets, and domain UI stay in `apps/ui/src/components`.
- Reuse `cn()` and shared primitives before creating new one-off UI helpers.
- Keep theme variables centralized in `shared/design-system/styles/globals.css`.
- If a component is only for station mode or admin mode, do not promote it to the design system.
